name: Ratcatcher
text: rush battlecry destroy a friendly minion and gain its attack and health
flavor: He's on the hunt for Togwaggle's missing rat.

name: Ravencaller
text: battlecry add two random 1 cost minions to your hand
flavor: That Friends and Familiars Plan is really paying off!

name: Tanglefur Mystic
text: battlecry add a random 2 cost minion to each player s hand
flavor: Doom!  Only doom for you!  But pay good tip, maybe less doom.

name: Toki, Time-Tinker
text: battlecry deal 3 damage to all minions and choose a passive treasure

name: Vivid Nightmare
text: choose a friendly minion summon a copy of it with 1 health remaining
flavor: "I… I dreamed I accidentally crafted a golden Millhouse! It was so REAL!"

name: Voodoo Doll
text: battlecry choose a minion deathrattle destroy the chosen minion
flavor: "Aww, I love it! It even kinda looks like me."

name: Walnut Sprite
text: echo
flavor: How do you make a walnut laugh? Crack it up!

name: Witch's Cauldron
text: after a friendly minion dies add a random shaman spell to your hand
flavor: Eye of murloc, ear of bat, foot of Fordring, fur of cat…

name: Witching Hour
text: summon a random friendly beast that died this game
flavor: The gates to the Gilnean pet cemetary MUST remain locked at all times.

name: Arcane Keysmith
text: battlecry discover a secret put it into the battlefield
flavor: She sells all manner of keys: from A flat to G sharp.

name: Bellringer Sentry
text: battlecry and deathrattle put a secret from your deck into the battlefield
flavor: "Who are you? Eh, none of my business."

name: Blood Witch
text: at the start of your turn deal 1 damage to your hero
flavor: Like a sloppy joe for vampires.

name: Dire Frenzy
text: give a beast 3 3 shuffle 3 copies into your deck with 3 3
flavor: It's always Huffer. And Huffer. And Huffer. And Huffer.

name: Felsoul Inquisitor
text: lifesteal taunt
flavor: Everyone expects an inquisition reference.

name: Fiendish Circle
text: summon four 1 1 imps
flavor: Like a knitting circle, but less evil.

name: Forest Guide
text: at the end of your turn both players draw a card
flavor: "Just sign this waiver, and we'll be on our way."

name: Houndmaster Shaw
text: your other minions have rush
flavor: They’re good dogs, Tess.

name: Lifedrinker
text: battlecry deal 3 damage to the enemy hero restore 3 health to your hero
flavor: In a pinch, he'll also settle for Holy Water: Zero.

name: Mad Hatter
text: battlecry randomly toss 3 hats to other minions each hat gives 1 1
flavor: He's entirely bonkers. All the best goblins are.

name: Militia Commander
text: rush battlecry gain 3 attack this turn
flavor: She only needs two commands: "Heel" and "Sic 'em!"

name: Mistwraith
text: whenever you play an echo card gain 1 1
flavor: One little Mistwraith sitting in a tree. M-I-S-T-I-N-G.

name: Night Prowler
text: battlecry if this is the only minion on the battlefield gain 3 3
flavor: Listen to the mew-sic of the night.

name: Sandbinder
text: battlecry draw an elemental from your deck
flavor: The secret is glue.

name: Scaleworm
text: battlecry if you re holding a dragon gain 1 attack and rush
flavor: A popular local alternative to bananas.

name: Spectral Cutlass
text: lifesteal whenever you play a card from another class gain 1 durability
flavor: So sharp it can cut through a spectral tomato!

name: Swift Messenger
text: rush each turn this is in your hand swap its attack and health
flavor: Same turn delivery - guaranteed!

name: Swift Messenger
text: rush each turn this is in your hand swap its attack and health

name: The Glass Knight
text: divine shield whenever you restore health gain divine shield
flavor: She seems scary, but she's got a glass jaw.

name: Totem Cruncher
text: taunt battlecry destroy your totems gain 2 2 for each destroyed
flavor: When regular totem hours won't cut it.

name: Toxmonger
text: whenever you play a 1 cost minion give it poisonous
flavor: Not all spiders are born poisonous. That's where he comes in.

name: Unpowered Steambot
text: taunt
flavor: Overpowered Steambot got nerfed.

name: Vex Crow
text: whenever you cast a spell summon a random 2 cost minion
flavor: As birds of ill omen, these crows often summon Doomsayers.

name: WANTED!
text: deal 3 damage to a minion if that kills it add a coin to your hand
flavor: Wanted: Dead or Undead.

name: Wing Blast
text: deal 4 damage to a minion if a minion died this turn this costs 1
flavor: Emeriss uses Wing Blast.  It's super effective!

name: Wispering Woods
text: summon a 1 1 wisp for each card in your hand
flavor: We didn't actually fire the guy who named Dark Wispers.

name: Witchwood Piper
text: battlecry draw the lowest cost minion from your deck
flavor: She rids villages of annoying pests, like rats and children.

name: Bewitched Guardian
text: taunt battlecry gain 1 health for each card in your hand
flavor: Amwitched. Beingwitched. Beenwitched.

name: Bonfire Elemental
text: battlecry if you played an elemental last turn draw a card
flavor: Next step: Marshmallow elementals.

name: Carrion Drake
text: battlecry if a minion died this turn gain poisonous
flavor: Fits easily into overhead luggage bins.

name: Chief Inspector
text: battlecry destroy all enemy secrets
flavor: Empty your pockets, I know you’ve got a Wandering Monster in there!

name: Clockwork Automaton
text: double the damage and healing of your hero power
flavor: Most mechs are pretty chill, but this one is all wound up.

name: Curio Collector
text: whenever you draw a card gain 1 1
flavor: Experts worry that curios are a gateway to face-collecting.

name: Darius Crowley
text: rush after this attacks and kills a minion gain 2 2
flavor: You either die a villain, or live long enough to see yourself become the hero.

name: Darius Crowley
text: battlecry deal 5 damage to all minions and choose a passive treasure

name: Deathweb Spider
text: battlecry if your hero took damage this turn gain lifesteal
flavor: The itsy bitsy spiders climbed up the village wall. Then came the witch and the spiders ate them all.

name: Dollmaster Dorian
text: whenever you draw a minion summon a 1 1 copy of it
flavor: The children were puzzled by the scratches covering the insides of their toy-boxes.

name: Duskfallen Aviana
text: on each player s turn the first card played costs 0
flavor: Someone called her "Tweety". She didn't take it well.

name: Festeroot Hulk
text: after a friendly minion attacks gain 1 attack
flavor: Tree puns arboring.

name: Ghostly Charger
text: divine shield rush
flavor: Maybe we should have called him Ghostly Rusher.

name: Holy Water
text: deal 4 damage to a minion if that kills it add a copy of it to your hand
flavor: For a healthier option, try Holy Water: Zero.

name: Muck Hunter
text: rush battlecry summon two 2 1 mucklings for your opponent
flavor: You think your job mucks.

name: Prince Liam
text: battlecry transform all 1 cost cards in your deck into legendary minions
flavor: "I have a very particular set of skills. Skills that make me a nightmare for witches like you."

name: Quartz Elemental
text: can t attack while damaged
flavor: These elementals, along with feldspar and mica, are often taken for granite.

name: Rotten Applebaum
text: taunt deathrattle restore 4 health to your hero
flavor: Key ingredient in Gilnean applesauce.

name: Vilebrood Skitterer
text: poisonous rush
flavor: It aspires to be a Vilebrood Dancer, but it has eight left feet.

name: Vilebrood Skitterer
text: poisonous rush poisonous rush

name: Witchwood Grizzly
text: taunt battlecry lose 1 health for each card in your opponent s hand
flavor: You know what they say about people with big hands? Small bears.

name: Coffin Crasher
text: deathrattle summon a deathrattle minion from your hand
flavor: Also does weddings.

name: Cursed Castaway
text: rush deathrattle draw a combo card from your deck
flavor: She was an ordinary castaway... until she found that cursed volleyball.

name: Deadly Arsenal
text: reveal a weapon from your deck deal its attack to all minions
flavor: Oh look. A Gorehowl.

name: Glinda Crowskin
text: minions in your hand have echo
flavor:
Summon an unlimited* number of minions!**


*Six
**Wisps

name: Lady in White
text: battlecry cast inner fire on every minion in your deck set attack equal to health
flavor: She was a lady in polka dots until the gnomish laundromat incident.

name: Mossy Horror
text: battlecry destroy all other minions with 2 or less attack
flavor: The hills have eyes. And teeth. Pretty bad breath, too.

name: Toki, Time-Tinker
text: battlecry add a random legendary minion from the past to your hand
flavor: Just a twist to the left, one quarter turn to the right and … oops! Well, we didn’t need that timeline anyway.

name: Azalina Soulthief
text: battlecry replace your hand with a copy of your opponent s
flavor: The cards are always golden on the other side.

name: Blackhowl Gunspire
text: can t attack whenever this minion takes damage deal 3 damage to a random enemy
flavor: The upper windows used to be for aiming. Then we thought: "Hey! MORE cannons!"

name: Bogshaper
text: whenever you cast a spell draw a minion from your deck
flavor: The tricky part is getting them to HOLD their shape.

name: Countess Ashmore
text: battlecry draw a rush lifesteal and deathrattle card from your deck
flavor: "1 minion… ah, ah, ah! 2 minions… ah, ah, ah! 3 minions… ah, ah, ah!"

name: Darkmire Moonkin
text: spell damage 2
flavor: Birds of a feather Moonfire together.

name: Furious Ettin
text: taunt
flavor: One head is a morning person. The other head hates morning people.

name: Lord Godfrey
text: battlecry deal 2 damage to all other minions if any die repeat this battlecry
flavor: Betrayed the Alliance. Betrayed the Horde. All for 200 achievement points and a sweet, sweet hat.

name: Nightscale Matriarch
text: whenever a friendly minion is healed summon a 3 3 whelp
flavor: Everywhelp, get in here!

name: Worgen Abomination
text: at the end of your turn deal 2 damage to all other damaged minions
flavor: Does anyone want to play dead!?

name: Wyrmguard
text: battlecry if you re holding a dragon gain 1 attack and taunt
flavor: They think they're trusted guardians. Dragons think they're convenient snacks.

name: Cauldron Elemental
text: your other elementals have 2 attack
flavor: Decorating tip: Unused cauldrons can make a lovely elemental display.

name: Deranged Doctor
text: deathrattle restore 8 health to your hero
flavor: Unfortunately, his doctorate is in Murloc Literature.

name: Gilnean Royal Guard
text: divine shield rush each turn this is in your hand swap its attack and health
flavor: Admittedly, they kind of dropped the ball with Prince Liam.

name: Gilnean Royal Guard
text: divine shield rush each turn this is in your hand swap its attack and health

name: Hagatha the Witch
text: battlecry deal 3 damage to all minions
flavor: Curse-bringer, tree-twister, mother of wretched things…Hanzo main.

name: Silver Sword
text: after your hero attacks give your minions 1 1
flavor: Silver’s malleability limits its utility as an edged weapon. On the other hand... SHINY!

name: Splintergraft
text: battlecry choose a friendly minion add a 10 10 copy to your hand that costs 10
flavor: We're going to need some bigger tweezers.

name: Splitting Festeroot
text: deathrattle summon two 2 2 splitting saplings
flavor: No use crying over split Festeroot,

name: Tess Greymane
text: battlecry replay every card from another class you ve played this game targets chosen randomly
flavor: Those who cannot remember their card history are doomed to repeat it.

name: Tess Greymane
text: battlecry deal 8 damage to all minions and choose a passive treasure

name: Shudderwock
text: battlecry repeat all other battlecries from cards you played this game targets chosen randomly
flavor: Beware the Shudderwock, my son. We're fresh out of vorpal daggers.

name: Emeriss
text: battlecry double the attack and health of all minions in your hand
flavor: Taste your world's corruption! It tastes like chicken.

name: Beakered Lightning
text: deal 1 damage to all minions overload 2
flavor: Working in a shaman's lab, it's important to be well-grounded.

name: Topsy Turvy
text: swap a minion s attack and health
flavor: "Help! I've fallen and I can't get down!"

name: Autodefense Matrix
text: secret when one of your minions is attacked give it divine shield
flavor: We call it the bubble machine.

name: Biology Project
text: each player gains 2 mana crystals
flavor: Step 1: Grow giant evil strawberry.\nStep 2: ????\nStep 3: Rule Azeroth!

name: Cloning Device
text: discover a copy of a minion in your opponent s deck
flavor: Zerek got sick of fighting over the remote.

name: Crystallizer
text: battlecry deal 5 damage to your hero gain 5 armor
flavor: This elf's winning the arms race.

name: Crystology
text: draw two 1 attack minions from your deck
flavor: "The Light is neither a particle nor a wave. It's more of a juice, really."

name: Eternium Rover
text: whenever this minion takes damage gain 2 armor
flavor: He's all beeps and smiles but you're just a walking pile of armor to him.

name: Faithful Lumi
text: battlecry give a friendly mech 1 1
flavor: They're a little light-headed.

name: Floop's Glorious Gloop
text: whenever a minion dies this turn gain 1 mana crystal this turn only
flavor: How much gloop could Floop's Gloop gloop if Floop's Gloop\ncould gloop gloop?

name: Glow-Tron
text: magnetic
flavor: They tried for weeks to make a stealth version, but eventually decided to just let it glow.

name: Goblin Bomb
text: deathrattle deal 2 damage to the enemy hero
flavor: They're Dr. Boom's babies. His baby boomers.

name: Mecharoo
text: deathrattle summon a 1 1 jo e bot
flavor: Its project name was KAN-GA. The little one was R-00.

name: Omega Assembly
text: discover a mech if you have 10 mana crystals keep all 3 cards
flavor: They told Dr. Boom he could only pick one. He disagreed.

name: Pogo-Hopper
text: battlecry gain 2 2 for each other pogo hopper you played this game
flavor: Once you hop, you just can't stop!

name: Secret Plan
text: discover a secret
flavor: The secret is... There is no plan!

name: Shooting Star
text: deal 1 damage to a minion and the minions next to it
flavor: Literally starstruck.

name: Skaterbot
text: magnetic rush
flavor: "See you later bot"\n- Jaina

name: Soul Infusion
text: give the left most minion in your hand 2 2
flavor: People called him a soulless monster. We're not sure this is better.

name: Spirit Bomb
text: deal 4 damage to a minion and your hero
flavor: Might take a few episodes to power up.

name: Test Subject
text: deathrattle return any spells you cast on this minion to your hand
flavor: “Now I feel... REALLY icky.”

name: The Soularium
text: draw 3 cards at the end of your turn discard them
flavor: Worst field trip ever.

name: Voltaic Burst
text: summon two 1 1 sparks with rush overload 1
flavor: Batteries have three components: Cathode, Anode, and Overload.

name: Astral Rift
text: add 2 random minions to your hand
flavor: Let's see what's behind rift number one!

name: Bomb Toss
text: deal 2 damage summon a 0 2 goblin bomb
flavor: Me throw face.

name: Celestial Emissary
text: battlecry your next spell this turn has spell damage 2
flavor: Casting with the stars.

name: Cloakscale Chemist
text: stealth divine shield
flavor: Her suit was fitted using a scale model.

name: Crystalsmith Kangor
text: divine shield lifesteal your healing is doubled
flavor: He wants to tank, but Boom always makes him play support.

name: Cybertech Chip
text: give your minions deathrattle add a random mech to your hand
flavor: Goes great with Cyber-Salsa.

name: Dead Ringer
text: deathrattle draw a deathrattle minion from your deck
flavor: Shortstop on N'zoth's softball team.

name: Demonic Project
text: each player transforms a random minion in their hand into a demon
flavor: Another group project where Jaraxxus doesn't do any work.

name: Dendrologist
text: battlecry if you control a treant discover a spell
flavor: He's teaching his little buddy to talk, but all it says is, "I am Gloop."

name: Elementary Reaction
text: draw a card copy it if you played an elemental last turn
flavor: It's just a Tempest Tantrum.

name: Fireworks Tech
text: battlecry give a friendly mech 1 1 if it has deathrattle trigger it
flavor: She learns by trial and error.  Mostly error.

name: Galvanizer
text: battlecry reduce the cost of mechs in your hand by 1
flavor: Also known as a power zinc.

name: Goblin Prank
text: give a friendly minion 3 3 and rush it dies at end of turn
flavor: "Ha ha! Glork looks ridiculous! ...Glork? Glork?"

name: Lab Recruiter
text: battlecry shuffle 3 copies of a friendly minion into your deck
flavor: Join the chemistry lab! We've got all the solutions.

name: Menacing Nimbus
text: battlecry add a random elemental to your hand
flavor: Electra stores her elementals in the cloud.

name: Omega Mind
text: battlecry if you have 10 mana crystals your spells have lifesteal this turn
flavor: Has a side-business selling her lipstick shade, "Omega Red."

name: Research Project
text: each player draws 2 cards
flavor: Abstract: Analyzing systemic applications of coldlight data sets vis-a-vis shuffle-related paradigms. Conclusion: Yay, cards!

name: Rocket Boots
text: give a minion rush draw a card
flavor: This is the happiest moment of Grik's life. We'll miss him.

name: Spark Engine
text: battlecry add a 1 1 spark with rush to your hand
flavor: He goes by Bzzzzt Aldrin.

name: Toxicologist
text: battlecry give your weapon 1 attack
flavor: Double-majoring in culinary sciences was definitely a mistake.

name: Unpowered Mauler
text: can only attack if you cast a spell this turn
flavor: After a stressful work day it really needs an outlet.

name: Upgradeable Framebot
flavor: *Awesome arm not included.

name: Venomizer
text: magnetic poisonous
flavor: Keeps getting banned for toxic behavior.

name: Violet Haze
text: add 2 random deathrattle cards to your hand
flavor: Elite Tauren Chieftain's next hit single.

name: Void Analyst
text: deathrattle give all demons in your hand 1 1
flavor: Conclusion: Nothing there.

name: Weapons Project
text: each player equips a 2 3 weapon and gains 6 armor
flavor: Harrison Jones was kicked off this project.

name: Whirliglider
text: battlecry summon a 0 2 goblin bomb
flavor: She's on a bomb voyage.

name: Augmented Elekk
text: whenever you shuffle a card into a deck shuffle in an extra copy
flavor: Her friends call her "Shuffleupugus".

name: Brainstormer
text: battlecry gain 1 health for each spell in your hand
flavor: Her hair was always like that.

name: Bronze Gatekeeper
text: magnetic taunt
flavor: "You have my shield! And the rest of me too."

name: Doubling Imp
text: battlecry summon a copy of this minion
flavor: What's worse than finding two imps in your lab? Only finding one of them.

name: Electra Stormsurge
text: battlecry your next spell this turn casts twice
flavor: "The coin? You used me for THE COIN!?"

name: Electrowright
text: battlecry if you re holding a spell that costs 5 or more gain 1 1
flavor: Carefully assembled from two Electrowrongs.

name: Extra Arms
text: give a minion 2 2 add more arms to your hand that gives 2 2
flavor: All the better to hug you with!

name: Kaboom Bot
text: deathrattle deal 4 damage to a random enemy minion
flavor: More Boom for your buck.

name: Landscaping
text: summon two 2 2 treants
flavor: We'll put a happy tree right here... and give him a little friend.

name: Microtech Controller
text: battlecry summon two 1 1 microbots
flavor: Best-selling author of "How to Make Friends You Completely Control."

name: Necrium Blade
text: deathrattle trigger the deathrattle of a random friendly minion
flavor: Grab death by the handle.

name: Nethersoul Buster
text: battlecry gain 1 attack for each damage your hero has taken this turn
flavor: Why did the demon cross the streams? To get to The Other Side.

name: Omega Medic
text: battlecry if you have 10 mana crystals restore 10 health to your hero
flavor: She feels waiting for healing makes you appreciate it more.

name: SN1P-SN4P
text: magnetic echo deathrattle summon two 1 1 microbots
flavor: "It's gonna be snip this, snap that. Bada-snip, bada-snap!"

name: Spider Bomb
text: magnetic deathrattle destroy a random enemy minion
flavor: Wrecks a dude, any size. Catches thieves, eats those guys. Look out! Here comes a Spider Bomb!

name: Spring Rocket
text: battlecry deal 2 damage
flavor: Proper grammar would be "sprung rocket."

name: Stargazer Luna
text: after you play the right most card in your hand draw a card
flavor: She's Dr. Boom's right-hand mage.

name: Unexpected Results
text: summon two random 2 cost minions improved by spell damage
flavor: Sometimes science is more art than science. A lot of people don’t get that.

name: Academic Espionage
text: shuffle 10 cards from your opponent s class into your deck they cost 1
flavor: The tenth Pyroblast really felt like overkill.

name: Annoy-o-Module
text: magnetic divine shield taunt
flavor: Every ten seconds it asks if you want to update.

name: Blightnozzle Crawler
text: deathrattle summon a 1 1 ooze with poisonous and rush
flavor: "Well we HAD it contained. Then you went and gave it legs!"

name: Coppertail Imposter
text: battlecry gain stealth until your next turn
flavor: It was fitting in fine until it gathered nuts and bolts.

name: Cosmic Anomaly
text: spell damage 2
flavor: INGREDIENTS: STAR-STUFF, \nBLUE #1, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS.

name: Explodinator
text: battlecry summon two 0 2 goblin bombs
flavor: When it absolutely, positively, has to blow up overnight.

name: Flobbidinous Floop
text: while in your hand this is a 3 4 copy of the last minion you played
flavor: Of all the scientists, he has the most knowledge (when measured in volume).

name: Harbinger Celestia
text: stealth after your opponent plays a minion become a copy of it
flavor: She wanders realities, taking on many forms. One was a unicorn princess.

name: Juicy Psychmelon
text: draw a 7 8 9 and 10 cost minion from your deck
flavor: It's not juicy at all. IT'S JUST MESSING WITH YOUR HEAD.

name: Necromechanic
text: your deathrattles trigger twice
flavor: If at first you don't succeed, die, die again.

name: Omega Defender
text: taunt battlecry if you have 10 mana crystals gain 10 attack
flavor: "Surrender. You have 10 mana to comply."

name: Piloted Reaper
text: deathrattle summon a random minion from your hand that costs 2 or less
flavor: New facial recognition systems keep out the Lorewalkers and Doomsayers.

name: Prismatic Lens
text: draw a minion and a spell from your deck swap their costs
flavor: Mined exclusively from the dark side of the moon.

name: Replicating Menace
text: magnetic deathrattle summon three 1 1 microbots
flavor:
It's a car!
*Whomp whomp whomp*
It's a robot!
*Whomp whom-CRUNCH*
It's… three.. smaller robots!

name: Steel Rager
text: rush
flavor: Rage alongside the machine.

name: Storm Chaser
text: battlecry draw a spell from your deck that costs 5 or more
flavor: Best drank after a stiff gale.

name: Thunderhead
text: after you play a card with overload summon two 1 1 sparks with rush
flavor: Most of his friends are still Metalheads.

name: Weaponized Piñata
text: deathrattle add a random legendary minion to your hand
flavor: It'll be fine.  It's not like they have any reason to hate us.

name: Whizbang the Wonderful
text: you start the game with one of whizbang s wonderful decks
flavor: From the prestigious Westfall Wonderfuls.

name: Crazed Chemist
text: combo give a friendly minion 4 attack
flavor: You don't have to be crazy to work here, but it helps.

name: Dyn-o-matic
text: battlecry deal 5 damage randomly split among all minions except mechs
flavor: Star player on the inter-office Boomball team.

name: E.M.P. Operative
text: battlecry destroy a mech
flavor:
"I said this looks like a job for me
So everybody just follow me
'Cause we need a little E.M.P.
'Cause it feels so mechy without me…"

name: Glowstone Technician
text: battlecry give all minions in your hand 2 2
flavor: "Windell! More light!"\n\n"I'm givin' it all she's got, Kangor!"

name: Holomancer
text: after your opponent plays a minion summon a 1 1 copy of it
flavor: Help me, worthy opponent. You're my only hope.

name: Loose Specimen
text: battlecry deal 6 damage randomly split among other friendly minions
flavor: You leave Deathstalker Rexxar alone in the lab for TWO minutes…

name: Mechano-Egg
text: deathrattle summon an 8 8 robosaur
flavor: When you need more iron in your diet.

name: Myra Rotspring
text: battlecry discover a deathrattle minion also gain its deathrattle
flavor: On her first day on the job, Myra removed the smoke detectors.

name: Myra's Unstable Element
text: draw the rest of your deck
flavor: What could go wrong?

name: Necrium Vial
text: trigger a friendly minion s deathrattle twice
flavor: Two near-death experiences for the price of one!

name: Omega Agent
text: battlecry if you have 10 mana crystals summon 2 copies of this minion
flavor: They don't just find the truth. They give it a ten second head start, then hunt it down.

name: Power Word: Replicate
text: choose a friendly minion summon a 5 5 copy of it
flavor: Available as a bundle, along with Power Words: Detonate, Animate, Annihilate, and Paper Weight.

name: Reckless Experimenter
text: deathrattle minions you play cost 3 less but die at end of turn cost can t be reduced below 1
flavor: It's hard to call her reckless when it's clear she knows what she's doing.

name: Rusty Recycler
text: taunt lifesteal
flavor: Ironic. It could recycle others, but not itself.

name: Seaforium Bomber
text: battlecry shuffle a bomb into your opponent s deck when drawn it explodes for 5 damage
flavor: Dress for the bomb you want, not the bomb you have.

name: Shrink Ray
text: set the attack and health of all minions to 1
flavor: Actually works by enlarging the rest of the world.

name: Subject 9
text: battlecry draw 5 different secrets from your deck
flavor: The original clever girl.

name: Supercollider
text: after you attack a minion force it to attack one of its neighbors
flavor: Boom's Second Law of Motion:\nHIT IT VERY HARD!

name: Wargear
text: magnetic
flavor: WAR! GEAR! What is it good for?

name: Zilliax
text: magnetic divine shield taunt lifesteal rush
flavor: Everything but the kitchen sink. Oh wait, there's one on his back.

name: Arcane Dynamo
text: battlecry discover a spell that costs 5 or more
flavor: We ran out of jars, so we started putting brains in other stuff.

name: Damaged Stegotron
text: taunt battlecry deal 6 damage to this minion
flavor: Sadly the warranty does not cover fireballs or acts of Boom.

name: Dr. Morrigan
text: deathrattle swap this with a minion from your deck
flavor: She will NOT STOP until she gets tenure.

name: Ectomancy
text: summon copies of all demons you control
flavor: "Zerek! Stay out of my lab!"

name: Eureka!
text: summon a copy of a random minion from your hand
flavor: Genius is 1% inspiration, and 99% drawing your Deathwing.

name: Mechanical Whelp
text: deathrattle summon a 7 7 mechanical dragon
flavor: "Well if I didn't build the whelp and YOU didn't build the whelp…"

name: Meteorologist
text: battlecry for each card in your hand deal 1 damage to a random enemy
flavor: Some say the world will end in fire. Some say in ice. Why not BOTH?

name: Missile Launcher
text: magnetic at the end of your turn deal 1 damage to all other characters
flavor: We asked, "Where do the missiles go?" and he answered, "Yes."

name: Security Rover
text: whenever this minion takes damage summon a 2 3 mech with taunt
flavor: Insecurity detected. Alerting hugbots.

name: Spark Drill
text: rush deathrattle add two 1 1 sparks with rush to your hand
flavor: Preferred weapon of Dr. Boom's orthodontist.

name: Tending Tauren
text: choose one give your other minions 1 1 or summon two 2 2 treants
flavor: That racial bonus to Herbalism finally paid off.

name: The Storm Bringer
text: transform your minions into random legendary minions
flavor: Finally, Electra can work from home.

name: Zerek, Master Cloner
text: deathrattle if you ve cast any spells on this minion resummon it
flavor: His original name was Aerek. Then the first clone was Berek. They went evil around Merek.

name: Astromancer
text: battlecry summon a random minion with cost equal to your hand size
flavor: All signs point to Antonidas.

name: Beryllium Nullifier
text: magnetic can t be targeted by spells or hero powers
flavor: Why Beryllium? Because it's hard to spell.

name: Boommaster Flark
text: battlecry summon four 0 2 goblin bombs
flavor: Every good plan requires a bit of patience. And a lot of explosives.

name: Dreampetal Florist
text: at the end of your turn reduce the cost of a random minion in your hand by 7
flavor: Unlike gnomes, dreampetals grow more than 3 feet tall.

name: Flark's Boom-Zooka
text: summon 3 minions from your deck they attack enemy minions then die
flavor: It used to be a Ba-zooka but we ran out of sheep.

name: Giggling Inventor
text: battlecry summon two 1 2 mechs with taunt and divine shield
flavor: "I shall build a mighty golden paladin! And he will GREET the WORLD!"

name: Gloop Sprayer
text: battlecry summon a copy of each adjacent minion
flavor: "Are you sure that's enough gloop?"\n\n"Hold on."

name: Kangor's Endless Army
text: resurrect 3 friendly mechs they keep any magnetic upgrades
flavor: "That's three, Kangor. Three isn't endless."\n- Countess Ashmore

name: Luna's Pocket Galaxy
text: change the cost of minions in your deck to 1
flavor: Luna became head of the astronomy department when her boss invented the Pocket Black Hole.

name: Star Aligner
text: battlecry if you control 3 minions with 7 health deal 7 damage to all enemies
flavor: "You're a Sagittarius? Me too! Just gimme a sec."

name: Bull Dozer
text: divine shield
flavor: Leave them alone for two minutes and they go right into sleep mode.

name: Dr. Boom, Mad Genius
text: battlecry for the rest of the game your mechs have rush
flavor: "Of course I've gone mad with power. Ever try going mad without it?"

name: Mulchmuncher
text: rush costs 1 less for each friendly treant that died this game
flavor: The latest advancement in\nhippo-botany.

name: The Boomship
text: summon 3 random minions from your hand give them rush
flavor: Dr. Boom ends his motivational speeches by dropping the mechs.

name: Zerek's Cloning Gallery
text: summon a 1 1 copy of each minion in your deck
flavor: Cloning can be a jarring experience.

name: Mecha'thun
text: deathrattle if you have no cards in your deck hand and battlefield destroy the enemy hero
flavor: "Your software will fail. Your users will abandon you. You are already obsolete."

name: Elemental Evocation
text: the next elemental you play this turn costs 2 less
flavor: It's just lighter fluid.

name: Pounce
text: give your hero 2 attack this turn
flavor: Comes with an overwhelming urge to jump into the nearest open box.

name: Regenerate
text: restore 3 health
flavor: Finally a cure for degenerates.

name: Bloodclaw
text: battlecry deal 5 damage to your hero
flavor: This weapon – ow! Requires a little – OWW! Finesse.

name: Daring Fire-Eater
text: battlecry your next hero power this turn deals 2 more damage
flavor: A few hours later he DESTROYED the arena bathrooms.

name: Devastate
text: deal 4 damage to a damaged minion
flavor: No thanks, I already devast-ate.

name: Grim Rally
text: destroy a friendly minion give your minions 1 1
flavor: There’s no “Aiiiieeee” in “Team.”

name: Gurubashi Chicken
text: overkill gain 5 attack
flavor: “Ya hold it by da feet, mon. Den ya THROW.”

name: Gurubashi Offering
text: at the start of your turn destroy this and gain 8 armor
flavor: For a limited time, loa blessings are on a pray-one-get-two deal (on selected sacrifices only).

name: Helpless Hatchling
text: deathrattle reduce the cost of a beast in your hand by 1
flavor: It can’t be all that helpful. Not wif dose widdle wings!

name: Saronite Taskmaster
text: deathrattle summon a 0 3 free agent with taunt for your opponent
flavor: Don't even think of asking for time off.

name: Serrated Tooth
text: deathrattle give your minions rush
flavor: The tooth hurts, don’t it?

name: Shriek
text: discard your lowest cost card deal 2 damage to all minions
flavor: The first warning sign of an oncoming warlock temper tantrum.

name: Spirit of the Dead
text: stealth for 1 turn after a friendly minion dies shuffle a 1 cost copy of it into your deck
flavor: Just because you’re dead doesn’t mean you’re off the team.

name: Spirit of the Raptor
text: stealth for 1 turn after your hero attacks and kills a minion draw a card
flavor: “Loti! LOTI! Drop it. Drop it Loti! Down! Down Loti!”

name: Spirit of the Rhino
text: stealth for 1 turn your rush minions are immune the turn they re summoned
flavor: Where did they get this preposterous hypothesis?

name: Springpaw
text: rush battlecry add a 1 1 lynx with rush to your hand
flavor: The terrible thing about lynxes is lynxes are terrible things. Their teeth are made out of biting, their paws are made out of springs!

name: The Beast Within
text: give a friendly beast 1 1 then it attacks a random enemy minion
flavor: Undoes years of obedience school training.

name: Totemic Smash
text: deal 2 damage overkill summon a basic totem
flavor: Trolls are the first group to have a totem survive atmospheric re-entry.

name: Wartbringer
text: battlecry if you played 2 spells this turn deal 2 damage
flavor: “Does she cause them with magic, or just…like have a bucket she brings with her?”

name: Auchenai Phantasm
text: battlecry this turn your healing effects deal damage instead

flavor: Murlocs practice Small Nice Voodoo.

They saw their fate a closin'
Aboard a pirate ship
On deck: The Howlin' Hozen
About to let one rip.

name: Dozing Marksman

flavor: It's the sleeper of the set.

name: Dragon Roar

flavor: Not to be confused with Dragon Yodel.

name: Firetree Witchdoctor
text: battlecry if you re holding a dragon discover a spell
flavor: If your tree is on fire - stop, drop, and troll.

name: Flash of Light
text: restore 4 health draw a card
flavor: Hey! No cameras allowed!

name: Headhunter's Hatchet
text: battlecry if you control a beast gain 1 durability
flavor: Zul'jin's primary recruiting tool.

name: Immortal Prelate
text: deathrattle shuffle this into your deck it keeps any enchantments
flavor:
She protec.
She attac.
But most importantly,
she come bac.

name: Likkim
text: has 2 attack while you have overloaded mana crystals
flavor: "I double frog dare you!"

name: Revenge of the Wild
text: summon your beasts that died this turn

name: Savage Striker

name: Scarab Egg

flavor: They say you can’t make an omelet without AHHH THEY’RE EATING MY FACE!

name: Serpent Ward
text: at the end of your turn deal 2 damage to the enemy hero
flavor: When snakes get sick, they get sent to the Serpent Ward.

name: Sharkfin Fan
text: after your hero attacks summon a 1 1 pirate
flavor: His taste in soup is criminal.

name: Shieldbreaker
text: battlecry silence an enemy minion with taunt
flavor: Can also break up fights, relationships, and unions.

name: Soup Vendor
text: whenever you restore 3 or more health to your hero draw a card
flavor: Fresh from the floor of the arena!

name: Spellzerker
text: has spell damage 2 while damaged
flavor: But don’t ask her to use it in a sentence.

name: Spirit of the Bat
text: stealth for 1 turn after a friendly minion dies give a minion in your hand 1 1
flavor: Nah nah nah nah, nah nah nah nah, nah nah nah nah, nah nah nah nah

name: Spirit of the Dragonhawk
text: stealth for 1 turn your hero power also targets adjacent minions
flavor: Dragonhawks aren’t known for their accuracy.

name: Stolen Steel
text: discover a weapon from another class
flavor: Because Thrall wouldn't lend me Doomhammer.

name: Waterboy
text: battlecry your next hero power this turn costs 0
flavor: 100% organic troll sweat.

name: Ankylodon
text: taunt

name: Banana Buffoon
text: battlecry add 2 bananas to your hand
flavor: You could say he has a certain appeal.

name: Bloodscalp Strategist
text: battlecry if you have a weapon equipped discover a spell
flavor: “Shoot them in the face” is more of a tactic than a strategy.

name: Bog Slosher
text: battlecry return a friendly minion to your hand and give it 2 2

flavor: “It’s an illusion, Malacrass!”

name: Haunting Visions
text: the next spell you cast this turn costs 3 less discover a spell
flavor: When you're awake at 3 AM and can't stop thinking about that time you called your teacher "mom."

name: High Priest Thekal
text: battlecry convert all but 1 of your hero s health into armor
flavor: "…and then I beat him with 1 Health!"

name: Masked Contender
text: battlecry if you control a secret cast a secret from your deck
flavor: Knew Mysterious Challenger back when he was a Mysterious Squire.

name: Master's Call
text: discover a minion in your deck if all 3 are beasts draw them all
flavor: "Hello? Yes, this is Huffer."

name: Ornery Tortoise
text: battlecry deal 5 damage to your hero
flavor: "Dude, where's my pizza?!"

name: Overlord's Whip
text: after you play a minion deal 1 damage to it
flavor: "This merit badge is for cruelty. This one's for whipping. And this one is for embroidery..."

name: Pterrordax
text: spell damage 1

name: Pyromaniac
text: whenever your hero power kills a minion draw a card
flavor: She prefers “Flammably Inclined.”

name: Ravasaur
text: poisonous stealth

name: Reckless Diretroll
text: taunt battlecry discard your lowest cost card
flavor: "Reck less!? ME WRECK MOAR!"

name: Sabertusk
text: rush

name: Sand Drudge
text: whenever you cast a spell summon a 1 1 zombie with taunt

name: Smolderthorn Lancer
text: battlecry if you re holding a dragon destroy a damaged enemy minion

name: Spirit of the Frog
text: stealth for 1 turn whenever you cast a spell draw a spell from your deck that costs 1 more
flavor: It is Wednesday, my dudes.

name: Spirit of the Lynx
text: stealth for 1 turn whenever you summon a beast give it 1 1

name: Splitting Image
text: secret when one of your minions is attacked summon a copy of it
flavor: Sometimes you get punched so hard they see double.

name: Surrender to Madness
text: destroy 3 of your mana crystals give all minions in your deck 2 2
flavor: Never give up, always surrender!

name: Time Out!
text: your hero is immune until your next turn
flavor: Highly effective against 3 year olds.

name: Untamed Beastmaster
text: whenever you draw a beast give it 2 2
flavor: All it takes is a tummy rub.

name: Wardruid Loti
text: taunt

name: Wardruid Loti
text: rush

name: Wardruid Loti
text: spell damage 1

name: Wardruid Loti
text: poisonous stealth

name: Wardruid Loti
text: choose one transform into one of loti s four dinosaur forms
flavor:
“Ravasaur!”
“Pretty scary”
“…Blammodax!”
“Is that a thing?”
“SMAXODON!”
“….now you’re just making those up.”

name: Wardruid Loti
text: taunt rush poisonous stealth spell damage 1

name: Zentimo
text: whenever you target a minion with a spell cast it again on its neighbors
flavor: Serenity. Peace. Many frogs.

name: Arena Fanatic
text: battlecry give all minions in your hand 1 1
flavor: Her fantasy Rumble league gives double points for dismemberment.

name: Arena Treasure Chest
text: deathrattle draw 2 cards
flavor: Yeah it's great, but did you see the Arena Treasure Arms?!

name: Griftah
text: battlecry discover two cards give one to your opponent at random
flavor: With Griftah in your deck, sometimes you start the game with The Coin!

name: Half-Time Scavenger
text: stealth overkill gain 3 armor
flavor: One player's trash is another's “Best In Slot”.

text: taunt lifesteal when you discard this add 2 copies of it to your hand
flavor: If you love Jeklik, set her free. YOU CAN'T GET RID OF HER.

name: Ice Cream Peddler
text: battlecry if you control a frozen minion gain 8 armor

name: Mark of the Loa
text: choose one give a minion 2 4 and taunt or summon two 3 2 raptors

name: Murloc Tastyfin
text: deathrattle draw 2 murlocs from your deck

name: Predatory Instincts
text: draw a beast from your deck double its health
flavor: Somebody’s been eating their funnel cakes.

name: Raiding Party
text: draw 2 pirates from your deck combo and a weapon
flavor: And a bowl of chips. And some of those little cocktail weenies!

name: Regeneratin' Thug
text: at the start of your turn restore 2 health to this minion
flavor: Regenerates any injury except heartbreak.

name: Rumbletusk Shaker
text: deathrattle summon a 3 2 rumbletusk breaker
flavor:
Rub a dub dub, three trolls in a tub.
And who do you think dey be?
Da Shaker, Da Breaker, and Da Undatakah.
And all of dem comin' for me.

name: Scorch
text: deal 4 damage to a minion costs 1 if you played an elemental last turn
flavor: The hoof.\nThe hoof.\nThe hoof is on fire.

name: Spirit of the Shark
text: stealth for 1 turn your minions battlecries and combos trigger twice

name: Spirit of the Tiger
text: stealth for 1 turn after you cast a spell summon a tiger with stats equal to its cost
flavor: Less of a cantrip and more of a cat-nip.

name: Ticket Scalper
text: overkill draw 2 cards
flavor: Takes ten percent off the top.

name: Walk the Plank
text: destroy an undamaged minion
flavor: Pirates will fall for anything.

name: War Master Voone
text: battlecry copy all dragons in your hand
flavor: War Master sounds cooler than Dragon Sitter.

name: Zandalari Templar
text: battlecry if you ve restored 10 health this game gain 4 4 and taunt 0 left ready
flavor: YOU WERE A TEMPLAR, JONDAR!

name: Arena Patron
text: overkill summon another arena patron
flavor: Everybody with a ticket get in here!

name: Baited Arrow
text: deal 3 damage overkill summon a 5 5 devilsaur
flavor: The card is common, but the steak is rare.

name: Blast Wave
text: deal 2 damage to all minions overkill add a random mage spell to your hand
flavor: If you’re burning and you know it, wave your hands!

name: Dragonmaw Scorcher
text: battlecry deal 1 damage to all other minions
flavor: Caution: Contains Flammable Material

name: Emberscale Drake
text: battlecry if you re holding a dragon gain 5 armor
flavor: The third little dragon made his armor out of adamantite.

name: Farraki Battleaxe
text: overkill give a minion in your hand 2 2
flavor: Only two things in life are certain: death and axes.

name: Former Champ
text: battlecry summon a 5 5 hotshot
flavor: The last time he saw action, Undertaker ruled the meta.

name: Gral, the Shark
text: battlecry eat a minion in your deck and gain its stats deathrattle add it to your hand
flavor: “… We’re gonna need a bigger board.”

name: Halazzi, the Lynx
text: battlecry fill your hand with 1 1 lynxes that have rush
flavor: Remember, you’re only as strong as your weakest lynx.

name: Mass Hysteria
text: force each minion to attack another random minion
flavor: Black Friday gets worse every year.

name: Mosh'Ogg Announcer
text: enemies attacking this have a 50 chance to attack someone else
flavor: One's play-by-play. The other is off-color.

name: Sightless Ranger
text: rush overkill summon two 1 1 bats
flavor: An eye for sore sights.

name: Snapjaw Shellfighter
text: whenever an adjacent minion takes damage this minion takes it instead
flavor: Nonono, the turtle is the Shellfighter.

name: Treespeaker
text: battlecry transform your treants into 5 5 ancients
flavor: Honestly, his delivery is a little wooden.

name: Arcanosaur
text: battlecry if you played an elemental last turn deal 3 damage to all other minions
flavor: Arcane energy… finds a way.

name: Cannon Barrage
text: deal 3 damage to a random enemy repeat for each of your pirates
flavor: Why fire your cannons strategically when you can fire them all at once?

name: Heavy Metal!
text: summon a random minion with cost equal to your armor up to 10
flavor: This metal is so heavy it will satisfy your iron requirements for the next year.

name: Krag'wa, the Frog
text: battlecry return all spells you played last turn to your hand
flavor: Krag'wa has a ritual to honor his friends and a ritual to devour his enemies. No one can tell them apart.

name: Mojomaster Zihi
text: battlecry set each player to 5 mana crystals
flavor: Sadly, she was still two credits short of her Witch Doctorate.

name: Rain of Toads
text: summon three 2 4 toads with taunt overload 3
flavor: "Oh, THAT'S how she brings the warts!"

name: Soulwarden
text: battlecry add 3 random cards you discarded this game to your hand
flavor: Reduce, reuse, resoul.

name: Stampeding Roar
text: summon a random beast from your hand and give it rush
flavor: [x]The Gurubashi Arena has an\nextremely permissive policy on\npets in the workplace.

name: Sul'thraze
text: overkill you may attack again
flavor: “Griftah here with de Sul’chop. One chop, you get four damage. Two chops, eight damage - you gonna change de way you fight."

name: A New Challenger...
text: discover a 6 cost minion summon it with taunt and divine shield
flavor: … Arrives? Approaches? TELL US ALREADY!

name: Amani War Bear
text: rush taunt
flavor: "I used to farm for hours! Now they just come in packs?"

name: Blood Troll Sapper
text: after a friendly minion dies deal 2 damage to the enemy hero
